text:
...Um
Is it okay if I stay a little longer today...?
There are some things I still want to practice...!

Oh
Using this place itself is not a problem.

That's a relief...!
Thank you very much!

...But are you sure you're okay?
Like, if you're tired or something...

No need to worry! I've been recovering properly
with daily meals, sleep, and treats!

I thought it could be a treat for
"Thanks for your hard work today," but

I thought maybe it would feel more appropriate
as a "Keep up the good work" gesture.

Thank you very much!
I truly appreciate your sentiment!
